  "title": "Commis / Chef de Partie / 5 Days/ Central- Japanese Restaurant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Japanese Restaurant - Looking for Commis / Chef de Partie</strong><br /><br /><strong>Working Hours:</strong></p><p>44 hours per week</p><p><strong>Work Days:</strong></p><p>5 days work, 2 off days</p><p><strong>Meals:</strong></p><p>Provided</p><p><strong>Location: </strong></p><p>Orchard,<br /><br /><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Assist Head and Sous Chefs to ensure smooth daily kitchen operations.</p></li><li><p>Prepare, portion, and present dishes according to recipes and standards.</p></li><li><p>Maintain awareness of all menu items, recipes, and presentation methods.</p></li><li><p>Check and ensure sufficient ingredients, equipment, and supplies for daily operations.</p></li><li><p>Store all food properly and handle ingredients safely.</p></li><li><p>Maintain high standards of kitchen cleanliness, hygiene, and safety.</p></li><li><p>Assist with equipment maintenance and regular cleaning.</p></li><li><p>Support inventory counts and record food wastage.</p></li><li><p>Collaborate with the kitchen team to deliver consistent, high-quality food.</p></li><li><p>Perform any other duties as assigned.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Basic Food Hygiene Certification </p></li><li><p>Prior kitchen experience is an advantage.</p></li><li><p>Team player with good communication and interpersonal skills.</p></li><li><p>Positive attitude, coachable, and eager to learn.</p></li></ul>",
